channel.title: MTM axocontrol set up question
channel.description:
Hello Everyone,
I just finished soldering the axo control from music thing modular and i wonder if there is a patch available that has all the controls mapped out? This is the first time i am actually using the axoloti.
Thank you in advance,
Ronny
